lead_paragraph: The Dallas Stars had only four road wins this season, and their test Tuesday night was compounded by having to travel to Arizona on game day because of a long flight delay. That forced them to hold a morning skate in Texas before finally taking off for Phoenix.

headline.print_headline: Lehtonen, Stars Win Testy Game vs Coyotes
